reviewText: this film is like a take on the classic snow white and the seven dworfs, but in this case you and 7 men trapped on an island and snow white is sasha montenegro. a latino chick with a nice butt and dosnt mind showing it. the movie could have been so much better than it was. but then again it might have been a porn film if they done it the way I wanted. she dosnt have a lot of nude scenes in this film actually only one scene that shows that magnificent butt of hers. a lot of breast shots. all in all not one of my fav at seeing her naked but the a good story line anyway. so if you can get it cheap go ahead and buy it. but like I said lacking in the nudity department.

There were some brief nude shots scattered through the movie.  The movie description suggests some sex scenes, but there aren't any.  Basically its one of those "I'll have sex with you if you kill everyone else" type plots were she turns everyone against each other.  Kind of a waste of money, but there were some good topless shots...
